    "ADVANCING WASHING TONS INTEREST PRICES SAG IN FEATURELESS SESSION Speculative Leaders Under PressureBulls Active in Specialty Group Copyright 194 by Cosmopolitan Nevi Barrie NEW YORK April 7ln a fairly active but featureless session of _ the stock market today the big speculative leaders receded to slightly lower levels while the bull ish efforts were occupied with a small number of the specialty stocks which have recently been bidding for public favor The market was largely in con trol of the professionals whose ac tivities accounted for most of the sales of the day New high prices for the year were recorded for American Water Works and Gen eral American Tank Car while weakness was most apparent in Pacific Oil Iron Products and Marine preferred On reports that directors of Iron Products Company contemplated re capitalization through the issuance f new 7 per cent preferred stocks and 13000000 in bonds that stock quickly declined three points It re covered most of this loss however when it was semiofficially stated that the bond issue plan will be abandoned _ The weakness in Pacific Oil was due to reports of overproduction in the California crude oil fields to which might be added the"
